snippet.title: DownFall Pre-Release Trailer
snippet.description:
The official pre-release trailer for DownFall, a FREE Half-Life 2 mod coming to Steam in April, 2017.

All links are listed below.


Steam Store:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/587650

Steam Greenlight:
http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=840088045

ModDB:
http://www.moddb.com/mods/downfall1

Marnamai's Portfolio:
http://marnamai.interlopers.net/

Music:
Mathias H. 'Rust' Pedersen - Intro Music / DownFall Soundtrack
Valve - Half-Life 2: Episode 2 Soundtrack


Trailer created by Niker107.
